{
  "stem": "214.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Around those Polish towns, you know, the big cities, especially, had those very narrow streets.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So there were several streets which were assigned to be ghettos, designated to be ghettos.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And on one side was a sidewalk, and the street in the middle-- what you call it here?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] You know, it's funny when you talk about those times I begin to think in Polish, because that's how I was living it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He-- so on one side, OK-- there was-- those-- there was a sidewalk and the street and the houses, where the-- which were not in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The other side of the street, only the houses-- houses, they were little shacks-- belonged to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and after all this was done, a short time later-- maybe it was-- I think that it was-- I'm almost sure that it was sort of around New Year's, after Christmas 1940, that they announced that the ghetto in Skierniewice is going to be liquidated because Skierniewice is going to become Judenrein, and you have to go.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't witness any-- any hangings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time in Skierniewice I don't think it was taking place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only thing that-- that, if you happen to find yourself in the street when you were coming across a German-- first of all, the Jew had to take off his hat for-- you know, in front of every German.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you didn't do it, or if he felt like beating you up, sometimes you would come home bloody.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I-- but in Skierniewice I didn't-- maybe they were taking place, I really wouldn't know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because one didn't run around the city.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
